      <title>美国就业岗位增加，美国制造业合同减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-unexpectedly-climb-us-manufacturing-contracts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份美国就业岗位空缺数量超出预期，增至三个月以来的最高水平 804 万，而制造业活动则连续第六个月萎缩。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-unexpectedly-climb-us-manufacturing-contracts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 14:20:51 GMT</pubDate>
