    <item>
      <title>波音公司考虑通过股票融资至少 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/boeing-considers-raising-at-least-10-billion-in-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，波音公司正考虑通过发行新股筹集至少 100 亿美元，以补充因持续罢工而进一步耗尽的现金储备。Siddharth Philip 在彭博电视台报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/boeing-considers-raising-at-least-10-billion-in-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 14:10:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国职位空缺数量攀升至三个月高点，超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-climb-to-three-month-high-exceeding-forecasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国八月份职位空缺数量增至三个月来的最高水平，这一发展与其他表明工人需求放缓的数据形成鲜明对比。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-job-openings-climb-to-three-month-high-exceeding-forecasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 14:02:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
